item.title: CVE-2018-12237|2024-09-16T16:28:04.698Z -- symantec%20corporation -- symantec%20reporter
item.description: The Symantec Reporter CLI 10.1 prior to 10.1.5.6 and 10.2 prior to 10.2.1.8 is susceptible to an OS command injection vulnerability. An authenticated malicious administrator with Enable mode access can execute arbitrary OS commands with elevated system privileges.
